The economic development bond program shall be administered by the secretary of the Cabinet for Economic Development. The board shall promulgate administrative regulations in accordance with KRS Chapter 13A for project selection criteria. The project selection criteria shall include, but not be limited to, the following:
Potential job creation or job retention;
Degree of public or private and local involvement;
Degree and conditions of project payback; and
Provision of child care assistance for employees' dependents aged twelve (12) years and younger. For the purpose of this section, child care assistance means onsite child care, child care information and referral, the purchasing of child care through vouchers or contracts, and any other form of child care assistance deemed applicable by the secretary.
